urdu transliteration text:
APNE BANDHE HAATHO KO, BIMAAR-KE ZEWARKO
BHULI NAHI MAI
@HujjatELC

THE RISING SANDSTORMS, THE BARREN LAND
uthti hui aandhi ko, mehshat ko bayaabakochupte huwe suraj ko, taariki ko maydaakochalte huwe khanjar koneze pe tere sar ko...
@HujjatELC

Lehrate Huwe Neza, Aur Shimr Ka Wo BarnaAa Aake Mere Peeche, Har Bibi Ka Wo ChupnaSholo Me Gire GharkoChinti Huwi Chaader Ko
ALL THE WOMEN COVERED BEHIND ME,
@HujjatELC

Hai Aaj Bhi Wo Giryaa, Hai Aaj Bhi Wo ZaariHai Aaj Bhi Pathar Ke, Sin-e Se Lahu JaariRote Huwe Pathar KoPathar Pe Rakhe Sarko, Bhuli
EVEN TODAY BLOOD FLOWS FROM THE STONE,
@HujjatELC
